  "originalDuration": 53.524875,
  "sentenceTimings": [
    {
      "sentenceIndex": 0,
      "text": "It is a truth universally acknowledged, that a single man in possession of a good fortune, must be in want of a wife.",
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 8.793,
      "duration": 8.793,
      "wordCount": 22
    },
    {
      "sentenceIndex": 1,
      "text": "However little known the feelings or views of such a man may be on his first entering a neighbourhood, this truth is so well fixed in the minds of the surrounding families, that he is considered the rightful property of some one or other of their daughters.",
      "startTime": 8.793,
      "endTime": 27.749,
      "duration": 18.956,
      "wordCount": 44
    },
    {
      "sentenceIndex": 2,
      "text": "The advantage of this persuasion is, that it fixes the attention of the young man on the most eligible matches.",
      "startTime": 27.749,
      "endTime": 35.957,
      "duration": 8.208,
      "wordCount": 19
    },
    {
      "sentenceIndex": 3,
      "text": "My dear Mr. Bennet, said his lady to him one day, have you heard that Netherfield Park is let at last?",
      "startTime": 35.957,
      "endTime": 43.661,
      "duration": 7.704,
      "wordCount": 20
    },
    {
      "sentenceIndex": 4,
      "text": "Mr. Bennet replied that he had not.",
      "startTime": 43.661,
      "endTime": 46.201,
      "duration": 2.541,
      "wordCount": 7
    },
    {
      "sentenceIndex": 5,
      "text": "But it is, returned she; for Mrs. Long has just been here, and she told me all about it.",
      "startTime": 46.201,
      "endTime": 53.139,
      "duration": 6.938,
      "wordCount": 18
    },
    {
      "sentenceIndex": 6,
      "text": "Mr. Bennet made no answer.",
      "startTime": 53.139,
      "endTime": 55.027,
      "duration": 1.887,
      "wordCount": 5
    },
    {
      "sentenceIndex": 7,
      "text": "Do you not want to know who has taken it? cried his wife impatiently.",
      "startTime": 55.027,
      "endTime": 60.036,
      "duration": 5.009,
      "wordCount": 14
    },
    {
      "sentenceIndex": 8,
      "text": "You want to tell me, and I have no objection to hearing it.",
      "startTime": 60.036,
      "endTime": 64.468,
      "duration": 4.433,
      "wordCount": 13
    }
  ],
